Package org.jivesoftware.openfire.crowd

Class Summary
CrowdAdminProvider Admin provider which will map a crowd group with openfire authorized admin users
CrowdAuthProvider Auth provider for Atlassian Crowd
CrowdGroupProvider Atlassian Crowd implementation of the GroupProvider.
CrowdManager  
CrowdProperties Reading the file crowd.properties which should be found in the conf folder of openfire
CrowdUserProvider Atlassian Crowd implementation of the UserProvider.
CrowdVCardProvider VCard provider for Crowd.
